The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the problem of single image dehazing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of deep learning models, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of perceptual losses and Laplacian pyramid suggests the involvement of graphics and visualization, which falls under cs.GR (Computer Graphics). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the use of generative models, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
